<html>
<body>

    <h2>Install Directories</h2>
    <ul>
        <li> Libraries will be installed in <code>/opt/flare/lib</code> </li>
        <li> Headers will be installed in <code>/opt/flare/include</code> </li>
        <li> Examples, documentation and CMake config files will be installed in <code>/opt/flare/share</code> </li>
    </ul>
    <p> For complete list of updates, visit <a href="http://www.flare.com/docs/releasenotes.htm">Flare Release Notes</a></p>

    <p> For questions about Flare or this installer, visit <a href="https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/flare-users"> Flare User Forums</a> </p>
</body>
</html>
